<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <HEAD>
        <META http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=euc-kr"> 
        <link rel = "stylesheet", href="/css/rating.css"/>    
        <!-- jquery CDN -->
        <script
        src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.js"
        integrity="sha256-QWo7LDvxbWT2tbbQ97B53yJnYU3WhH/C8ycbRAkjPDc="
        crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery-cookie/1.4.1/jquery.cookie.js"></script>
        <!-- qrcode 라이브러리 CDN -->
        <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/qrcodejs/1.0.0/qrcode.min.js" integrity="sha512-CNgIRecGo7nphbeZ04Sc13ka07paqdeTu0WR1IM4kNcpmBAUSHSQX0FslNhTDadL4O5SAGapGt4FodqL8My0mA==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></script>
        <TITLE> Healing Rating Page</TITLE> 
        <SCRIPT LANGUAGE="JavaScript"> 
            function Timer() { 
                setTimeout("locateKap()",25000); 
            } 
            function locateKap(){
                location.replace("/");
            }
            cnt = 25; // 카운트다운 시간 초단위로 표시
            function countdown() {
                if(cnt == 0){
                    // 시간이 0일경우
                    locateKap();
                } else {
                    // 시간이 남았을 경우 카운트다운을 지속한다.
                    document.all.count_text.innerHTML = cnt + "초후에 힐링 화면으로 이동합니다..";
                    setTimeout("countdown()",1000);
                    cnt--;
                }
            }
        </SCRIPT> 
    </HEAD> 
    <BODY onLoad="Timer();">
      <div id="container">
        <div id="content" class ="container-max">
            <h1>방금 제공 받으신 서비스, 어떠셨나요?</h1>
            <p>축적된 별점데이터를 기반으로 저희의 모바일웹 "Healing4U"를 통해 사용자분들께 광고서비스를 추천해드리고 있습니다.</p>
        </div>
        <div id="button_grp">
            <h2 style='display:none;'><%= userID %></h2>
            <script>
                let userIdTag = document.querySelector('#button_grp h2');
                let userId = userIdTag.innerText;
            </script>
            <button type="button" class="like" value="1" onclick="buttonClicked(this.value, userId)">
                <img id = "btn_img" src="https://cdn4.iconfinder.com/data/icons/business-solid-the-capitalism/64/Like-512.png">
            </button>
            <button type="button" class="unlike" value="0" onclick="buttonClicked(this.value, userId)">
                <img id = "btn_img" src="https://cdn4.iconfinder.com/data/icons/business-solid-the-capitalism/64/Unlike-512.png">
            </button>
        </div>
        <div class="text">
            <span id="count_text"></span>
            <br>
            <span>더 많은 서비스를 제공받고 싶다면, 오른쪽 QR코드를 이용하세요.</span>
        </div>
        <div id="qr"></div>
        <script type="text/javascript">
            new QRCode(document.getElementById("qr"), "http://13.125.36.224:2004/");
        </script>

      </div>
        <script>countdown();</script>
        <script src="/js/rating.js"></script>
    </BODY> 
</html>